import { ReactNode } from 'react'
import { Header } from '../Header'
import * as C from './styles'
import {SidebarItem} from '../SidebarItem'


type Props = {
  children: ReactNode
}

export const Theme = ({children} : Props) => {
  return (
    <C.Container>
      <C.Area>
        <Header/>

        <C.Steps>
          <C.Sidebar>
            <SidebarItem
              title='Pessoal'
              description= 'Se identifique'
              icon='pro'
            />
          </C.Sidebar>
          <C.Page>
            {children}
          </C.Page>
        </C.Steps>
      </C.Area>
    </C.Container>
  )
}
